---
import SiteLayout from "../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="YouTube & Social Media Creators | PoliceConduct.org"
  pagePath="/partner/creator/"
>
  <main class="flex-grow-1">
    <section class="py-vh-3 bg-gray-100 border-bottom border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <ol class="breadcrumb mb-3">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item">
              <a class="link-dark" href="/partner/">Partners</a>
            </li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Creator</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-end">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
            <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-2">
              Value proposition
            </p>
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">The Creator Intelligence Hub</h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted mb-0">
              PoliceConduct.org is the back-end for professional investigations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="text-uppercase small text-muted">Built for</div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">
                  YouTubers and social media influencers
                </div>
                <div class="text-muted small">
                  Use structured data to find high-value audits and build cases
                  that hold up.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-7">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold">
              1. The creator dashboard: investigative intelligence
            </h2>
            <p class="text-muted">
              Stop guessing where the next story is. Use the heat map and
              pattern tools to find precincts and officers with behavior
              patterns that suggest likely First Amendment violations.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0 d-flex flex-column gap-2">
              <li>Heat map lead generation with anonymized trend spikes.</li>
              <li>
                Pattern filters for refusal-to-identify or
                interference-with-filming reports.
              </li>
              <li>
                Case file links with deep-link tracking (example:
                /case/TX-9982).
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-3">
                <div class="text-uppercase small text-muted">
                  Business intelligence
                </div>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  We provide the data; you provide the footage. Find the next
                  audit with fewer miles and more impact.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-secondary rounded-0 border-dark mt-4 mb-0">
          Example: A 400% spike in illegal detention reports in a single county
          can surface your next high-impact story.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2 bg-light border-top border-bottom border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">
          2. Case file links for retention and SEO
        </h2>
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Case file links
                </p>
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold">Keep audiences engaged</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Give viewers a dedicated report link that houses evidence,
                  officer history, and relevant statutes after the video ends.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Subscriber updates
                </p>
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold">Extend the story life</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Let audiences subscribe to report updates, keeping your
                  investigation active long after upload day.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">
          3. The legal partner portal: building the Monell case
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Aggregated reports across a department help support Monell claims by
          showing a custom or policy of misconduct.
        </p>
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Discovery evidence logs
                </p>
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold">Find other witnesses</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Locate related reports involving the same officer or precinct
                  to build an evidentiary chain.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Department history
                </p>
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold">Prove deliberate indifference</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Show city leaders a pattern of verified reports to establish
                  the moving-force evidence required for Monell liability.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2 bg-gray-100 border-top border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">4. Why collaborate with us?</h2>
        <div class="table-responsive">
          <table class="table table-bordered align-middle">
            <thead class="table-light">
              <tr>
                <th scope="col">Partner need</th>
                <th scope="col">Our platform's solution</th>
                <th scope="col">Why it scales your business</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>High-value targets</strong></td>
                <td>Trend analytics and heat maps.</td>
                <td>Optimizes filming schedules for the best legal stories.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Monetization safety</strong></td>
                <td>Off-platform evidence text and links.</td>
                <td>Protects revenue while enabling deep-dive detail.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Legal success</strong></td>
                <td>Pattern-of-conduct data.</td>
                <td>Turns a single case into a Monell-ready record.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Audience loyalty</strong></td>
                <td>Subscribe-to-case notifications.</td>
                <td>Converts one-time viewers into long-term followers.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-start">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Partner tools & assets
                </p>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold mb-0">Resource kit</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                  Templates and assets that help creators and attorneys publish
                  responsibly.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
            <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">
              <div class="border-start border-dark ps-3">
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">
                  Case file description templates
                </h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Pre-written blurbs for YouTube descriptions that direct
                  viewers to a verified case file and subscription updates.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-start border-dark ps-3">
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">Verified auditor badge</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  A digital seal that shows you rely on verified public records
                  and structured reporting standards.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-start border-dark ps-3">
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">Statute cheat sheet</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  A dynamic list of common citations (42 U.S.C. ยง 1983, First
                  and Fourth Amendment case law) to keep reports legally
                  precise.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-secondary rounded-0 border-dark">
              "This interaction has been logged at PoliceConduct.org (Case
              #12345). Visit the case file to see the officer's history, read
              related legal statutes, and subscribe for updates on this
              investigation."
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-7">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-1">Founding Partner program</h2>
            <p class="text-muted mb-0">
              Early partners can earn a Verified Analyst profile to endorse
              legal accuracy and elevate investigative standards.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="text-uppercase small text-muted">
                  Verified analyst track
                </div>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Ask about the Code of Ethics and verification process to
                  access the badge.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div
          class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row align-items-lg-center justify-content-between gap-3"
        >
          <div>
            <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-1">
              Ready to build the Creator Intelligence Hub?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-muted mb-0">
              We can share a partner resource kit with templates for linking
              your videos.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="btn btn-dark rounded-0"
            href="/about/contact?whoami=Partner&message=I%27m%20interested%20in%20a%20creator%20partner%20resource%20kit%20and%20case%20file%20link%20templates."
          >
            Request the resource kit
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
